  %% S007-RENDER-FIX: the GUEST owns its socket through JoinScreen, so a survivor
  %% (guest) receives opponent-disconnected as a normal MESSAGE frame over the
  %% JoinScreen socket. JoinScreen MUST forward it to GameRoot's handler (routing
  %% parity with board-update/game-over) or the frame is dropped and the survivor
