  %% the first edition — the defect UC1's stand-up probe found. Marked now.
  spaJoinScreen["spa-join-screen<br/>src/app/src/game/JoinScreen.tsx — guest socket owner<br/>forwards game-ready/board-update/game-over/opponent-disconnected to GameRoot"]:::s007changed
  spaJoinScreen -->|forwards opponent-disconnected frame| spaOnlineDisconnect
  linkStyle 15 stroke:#1565c0,stroke-width:3px;

